--------------
Return a JSON object with this exact structure:
{
  "analysis_summary": [
    {
      "item_id": "string",
      "issue_found": true/false,
      "issue_types": ["wrong_balance", "status_mismatch"],
      "explanation": "Brief explanation citing specific fields"
